arStrings.szText: "I want to increase the potency of my healing potion."
Well, you certainly have the look of someone who spends a lot of time in the wilds. I expect you'll also want some of my elixirs, but let's focus on your healing potion for now.
I have some extra materials we can use this time. If you want to improve your healing potion further or craft any elixirs, you'll need to source your own ingredients.
I'll not leave these walls... never again.
"I'll not leave these walls, never again." is Fearful
